snippet.title: Deep Space Outpost - Alt Version Trailer
snippet.description:
Alternative version of the trailer I put out a couple of days ago. Have sped up the building part and trimmed some of the other footage, making it closer to a minute in length. 

Free prototype is on itch to download and play.
Itch: https://niris.itch.io/deep-space-outpost
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/NirisGames
